---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Literary Autumn Blog">
	<h1>About the Author</h1>
	<img src="/author-photo.jpg" alt="Author's photo" class="author-photo">
	<p>
		Welcome to my autumn-inspired literary blog. I'm a passionate writer who finds inspiration in the changing colors of fall, 
		the crisp air, and the cozy atmosphere that comes with the season. Through my writing, I aim to capture the essence of autumn 
		and share stories that resonate with the soul.
	</p>
	<p>
		My work spans various genres, from poetry to short stories and personal essays. Each piece is infused with the warmth and 
		nostalgia that autumn brings, exploring themes of change, reflection, and the beauty found in life's transitions.
	</p>
	<p>
		Thank you for joining me on this literary journey through the autumn of our lives and imaginations.
	</p>
</Layout>

<style>
	h1 {
		color: rgb(var(--accent));
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.author-photo {
		float: right;
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 50%;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 1rem;
	}
	p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
</style>